sentences: In May 2013, he attended the Red Bull Music Academy in New York City where he was able to meet and collaborate with people in contrast to how he described his origin as "this small town where there's no one doing what I was trying to do, you're not really sure if it's an actual thing you're doing".
After releasing several EPs and being signed to Brainfeeder Records, Dinther released his first full-length album Fool in May, 2016.
